    "name": "Fate of the Pharaoh",
    "steam_appid": 1754790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754790/extras/42c594173ce96eea76a0a27e3d1b762d.avif?t=1765364611\" width=630 height=630 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The glorious Egyptian empire is left exhausted after a longstanding war. The greedy invaders fled, leaving chaos and ruins of a once magnificent kingdom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the loyal Pharaoh’s adviser and help him to restore peace and prosperity in the golden cities of Egypt. Construct houses re-establish production, collect taxes and gather materials, set up production and trade, and fight crocodiles and wicked cobras. Can you return Egypt to its days of glory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754790/extras/595b6d44058cf65776e62d739da17007.avif?t=1765364611\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 Dozens of levels packed with city building fun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏰 Build, upgrade, and defend your towns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡ Use powerful boosts &amp; unlock achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 Intriguing narrative — a plot with twists and memorable characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ 3 difficulty levels – from relaxed exploration to true challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📴 Play completely offline — anytime, anywhere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔒 No data collection — your privacy is safe</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹 Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click / Tap to gather resources, build houses, manage workers, and keep your people thriving as you progress through each level. Use boosts when things get tough — but the real reward is mastering strategy and efficiency!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Play your way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand, optimize, upgrade, and develop your settlements the way you like. Customizable challenge — Relaxed, Standard, and Extreme difficulty modes. Earn Achievements as you complete objectives and perfect your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌌 Immersive adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mix of colorful art, atmosphere, and story-rich progression paired with satisfying time-management and city-building mechanics. Whether you enjoy calm, casual resource gathering or intense strategic challenges — this game delivers both.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754790/extras/655253165d6364c944cdf7e1c87a2b52.avif?t=1765364611\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > HELP the people of ancient Egypt to restore their kingdom </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > EXPLORE the magnificent era of our history</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 44 EXCITING levels to master and hundreds of quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > FIGHT dangerous cobras, scorpions, crocodiles and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > EARN achievements along the way</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > MEET friends from outer space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2 difficulty modes: relaxed and adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Step-by-step tutorials for beginners</p></li></ul>",
